  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a push box game. Players will control a cute little squirrel to collect acorns to help it survive the cold winter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/f5fe12d5d15709313f95d2373e4c443f.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/f5fe12d5d15709313f95d2373e4c443f.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the general Sokoban game, the game adds some unique designs. Including movable obstacles, removable obstacles, and the interaction between different obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wood can be pushed into the river to form a bridge:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild boars can destroy shrubs:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also warmly provides answers to puzzles for players who are not good at this type of game, as long as you can put in a period of effort on your own first. The time required to unlock the answer for each level is different, generally the more difficult it is, the longer it takes. But please don’t worry, it will not exceed 10 minutes at most</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The play button in the lower right corner can play the complete answer:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2578225429bae3877b284cfcf0ca6d39.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/2578225429bae3877b284cfcf0ca6d39.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a push box game. Players will control a cute little squirrel to collect acorns to help it survive the cold winter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/f5fe12d5d15709313f95d2373e4c443f.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/f5fe12d5d15709313f95d2373e4c443f.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the general Sokoban game, the game adds some unique designs. Including movable obstacles, removable obstacles, and the interaction between different obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wood can be pushed into the river to form a bridge:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/4b5575663bad363022eaf2b784588545.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild boars can destroy shrubs:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2b43eb4bf76e0622d099dc0f1b9fe07c.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also warmly provides answers to puzzles for players who are not good at this type of game, as long as you can put in a period of effort on your own first. The time required to unlock the answer for each level is different, generally the more difficult it is, the longer it takes. But please don’t worry, it will not exceed 10 minutes at most</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The play button in the lower right corner can play the complete answer:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2578225429bae3877b284cfcf0ca6d39.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/2578225429bae3877b284cfcf0ca6d39.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
